Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,KILLVEARN'S TRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Calamity Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's completely focused on the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's completely forgotten about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever done that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To try to dodge my Calamity Wall\Nby standing in its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My body just reacted instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know I could use\Nmy Dragonic Aura that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it,\Nit's just like with my Doru Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like I could just do it naturally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Leona! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised you that\NI'd take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're out of breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!\NJust focus on the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Dai can do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was going to focus on healing him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I may not even have a role in this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about it,\Nbut it looks like you're right, Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel something unimaginable\Nawakened inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like when I first gained\Nthe power of my Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might actually be able\Nto match you in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your strength nearly matches my own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How selfless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To possess such power, and not think\Nwhat you should do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be blunt, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power can decide\Nthe fate of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I was ever wary of Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He possessed the Combat Instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An opponent who fights unpredictably
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone I would rather not fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if someone is that powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to see it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to... waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you are more powerful\Nthan the Dragonoid Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With the power of your second Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you have gained\Nthe Combat Instincts of all past Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are more powerful\Nthan anyone I have ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say you're the first\Nto ever get this close to my level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will you be my servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Why would...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer your father gave\Nto this question was "Yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was a pure Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran understood\Njust how ugly and foolish humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are disgusting, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't worth lending your power to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fight for them\Nand happen to win, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be willing to bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,should you defeat me and return to\Nthe humans, you will suffer persecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They only come crying to you\Nwhen they are in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once peace settles,\Nthey begin to complain and accuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will be\Nstripped of your title as Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't want someone who is not\Npure human to stand above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,only because you hold\Na personal affinity for Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no different from Baran's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of one individual cannot\Nchange something as nebulous as a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As royalty, you should know this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not discriminate between races\Nfor those who are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran and Hadorra may have betrayed me,\Nbut I still respect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what now, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you risk your life\Nfor a worthless victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you serve one\Nwho understands your true value?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a child,\Nbut the choice should be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What will it be, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A child indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You still cling to\Nthe sweet illusion of being a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that humans can sometimes be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you're lying about what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I still love everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I love all the creatures of\Nthe Surface World who made me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you say is really true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's what the people\Nof the Surface World want...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are a blessing for these humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To make the almighty Dragon Knight\Nsay such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they are quite sinful creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to learn a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That to side with them\Nwas your greatest folly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai... Please win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not for anyone else. But for yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how, but you seem to know\Nwhat's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clearly trying to rush this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're\Nnearly done, Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban... I didn't expect\Nthis much from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment you decided to hold this duel,\Nyou put yourself at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have one way of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To deceive and snare. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your numerous tools and traps,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you immobilize your target\Nand dispatch them easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Reaper, it's a sure way of killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but over the years,\Nyou've lost the ability to win fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your strength, skill,\Nand speed are all top-rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but your deciding attacks\Nlack the drive to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't mortally wound\Nsomeone like me who can match your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave in to the humiliation\Nof your wounded pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By using this duel with the Judge,\Nyou already sealed your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose, Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are quite fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, I can't win\Nwithout any traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I really wanted to, I could train\Nand be unbeatable in a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strong enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've lost interest in such victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an insect caught in a spider's web,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing a target caught\Nin a trap is glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The more someone has worked hard, the more\NI love seeing them fall into my traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I've tasted that joy,\Nkilling in other ways seems foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I can effortlessly finish them off\Nand grant them peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me truly feel\Nthat I'm indeed a Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met an enemy\Nas fiendish as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My sword suddenly broke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I felt it hit something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It didn't break. It was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said,\Ndeceiving and snaring is how I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I set up a snare in secret\Nwhile we were fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had been more observant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have noticed the lines\Non my hat have been fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Invisible blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The lines on my hat\Ncontain invisible blades
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that once drawn will finish an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They are hidden all around this field!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A cage made of 13 invisible blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kilban's final trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Phantom Razor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, it's your turn\Nto prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAGAMU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,REAPER FLUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge carelessly\Nand it could end up killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least die to my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A single stab to the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me fiendish,\Nbut you'll thank me when I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for freeing me from this hell."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I'm losing consciousness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a terrifying trap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't attack or defend like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either way, I'm certain to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never wanted to use this again,\Nbut I can't let him escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Megante, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Judge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can commit suicide with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this Judge was part of your...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Teaming up with the Judge\Nis a terrible trap indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I made such preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I even altered it to self-destruct\Nalong with this field if needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can use Megante, too?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,See? In the end, using traps\Nis the best way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vengeance complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops, this isn't the White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Baran died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the shock\Nof the explosion shifted my exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that\NKing Ban is fighting Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dai is winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. There's no need\Nto rush to rescue King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai defeats him then that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be obligated to help him,\Nbut I'm not duty-bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly the final battle.\NAnd the end of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And who will end me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You showing up here changes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Crocodine\Nor that rat can harm me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Ron Berku or Larhart\Ncould damage my ultimate body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,None in this world can end me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You or Aban may have had a chance,\Nbut Aban is currently fighting Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master is...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are already beyond recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can do anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There's one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He means me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've completely\Njoined these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made a promise with Hyunckel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd defeat everyone\Nhe was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it's time to die, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not someone a puppet\Nwith a tough body can do anything about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this, Larhart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike when we met, I'm at full power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my strength at its best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A metallic life form using Aura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible! It's inconceivable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fight an enemy\Nwithout your Captain's permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me permission, mister Captain.\NCan I beat the pulp out of this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-It worked?!\N-That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's impressive speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Added with the hardness of Orichalcum\Nand the power of Aura...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may have been severely\Nunderestimating this one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, that Aura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym's Aura is neither Dark Aura,\Nnor Dark Fire Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Aura of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really is Aura of Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hym was in the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even during our duel,\NHym was already emitting Aura of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Going beyond good and evil,\Nand seeking only to settle things with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym was no longer evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! Aura of Light is the greatest\Nweakness for Mystban who uses Dark Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could defeat Mystban\Nas easily as Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a huge find!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going! Keep it up Little Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Little Hym"?! What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving names like that\Nis the custom of my commandos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you come up\Nwith a better name than that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Hym... Hymmy... Hymster...\NWhich do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'll take Little Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym's one of the strongest of us and\NChiu's treating it like it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a fascinating rat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curses! This pathetic puppet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now finish him, Little Hym! Or would you\Nprefer Pawny, since you're a pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Call me whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you all to shreds!\N{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me your little tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hym had to do was stamp one foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Field was shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me like a man, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow! Hym's actually amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm shocked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't imagine Hym possessed such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can really win?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enveloped in Aura of Light,\NHym is unaffected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field\Nand closes in on Mystban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dai continues\Nto hold an advantage over Ban,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Dai can't help but feel nervous\Nat Ban's confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As uneasy air swirls,\Ncan Dai and friends achieve victory?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Deciding Attack"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
